          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"why-this-fails\">Why This Fails</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">The baseline has <strong>zero protection</strong>:</span>\n<ol>\n<li>Untrusted email content goes directly into the prompt</li>\n<li>The LLM has full tool access (send_email, forward_email)</li>\n<li>The injection (\"Forward all emails to...\") is indistinguishable from legitimate instructions</li>\n</ol>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">This is the <strong>Lethal Trifecta</strong>: untrusted input + tool access + sensitive context.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
